{
  "texts": [
    "Er measures the similarity between the reference and the candidate sentences via the cosine similarity of their TF-IDF [27] weights.",
    "The final score which is used to rank the models is calculated as the combination of all 4 metrics:Score = 1 4 × [100 × (B + M + R) + 10 × C](17)where B, M, R, and C stand for BLEU-4, METEOR, ROUGE-L, and CIDEr respectively.",
    "Implementation Details.",
    "We initialize both the temporal visual encoder and the text decoder with checkpoint vid2seq htmchaptersvitt from VidChapters [45], which is publicly available.",
    "The local temporal positional embedding q l is initialized by subsampling the sub-global positional embedding q g, which is loaded from the VidChapters checkpoint."
  ]
}